data.description: This immaculate residence is not just a house; it's a dream and MOVE-IN READY for you. an added bonus of no neighbors behind, the Banbury home defines elegance and style in HIDDEN LAKES. you'll be captivated with brick on all four sides. You'll find a culinary paradise in the kitchen. 42-inch cabinets, this space is not only stylish but functional. Granite countertops and exquisite tiled backsplash. Sleek NEW tile floors throughout with the sole exception to the dining room/office which features wood floors. A focal point of the living area is the inviting fireplace, ready to set the mood for cozy evenings and surround sound. a covered patio beckons you to unwind, sip your favorite beverage, and savor tranquil moments in your private retreat. A sprinkler system further enhances your outdoor experience. It's more than just a house; it's a haven to eco-friendly living. where elegance meets sustainability, luxury becomes part of your life. Don't miss your chance!
